        p.section__item__description
          | A beautiful online IDE with a friendly social user experience - we believe coding interview preparation should be fun!
      .section__item
        img.section__item__img(src="/chat.png")
        h3.section__item__title Video and Text Chat
        p.section__item__description
          | Connect you with tech experts for live help via video, and text chat.
      .section__item
        img.section__item__img(src="/video.png")
        h3.section__item__title Room Playback
        p.section__item__description
          | Record the entire interview, every keystroke, each code execution and the related output. Playback the session later, as often as you want.
